==Miss World==
The '''Miss World'''<ref>http://www.missworld.com/</ref> pageant began in 1951 and since then '''Puerto Rico''' has had 15 representatives classify in the finals, including 2 winners, 2 runners-up, 10 semi-finalists and 1 quarter-finalist.
