==Miss Universe==
The '''Miss Universe'''<ref>http://www.missuniverse.com/</ref> pageant began in 1952 and since then '''Puerto Rico''' has had 20 representatives classify in the finals, including 5 winners, 7 runners-up, 6 finalists and 2 semi-finalists. With 5 wins, '''Puerto Rico''' is the third country with the most wins behind '''USA''' (8 wins) and '''Venezuela''' (7 wins).
